 <h1 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
  <span style="font-weight: 400">
   <font size="5">
    American Sign Language: "Russia"
   </font>
  </span>
  <br/>
 </h1>
 <p>
  <br/>
  To sign "Russia," drag the side of your index finger backwards across your chin, 
then flick the finger downward.  Think of wiping "ale" from your chin and 
flinging it to the floor.
